<TEXT>
   A bank will issue a series of designer
MasterCards to commemorate the 50th anniversary of ``Gone With the
Wind,'' and cable TV mogul Ted Turner will get the first one.
   Citizens and Southern National Bank in Atlanta will issue the
first of the cards this month to coincide with the 50th anniversary
